title: High Plat Support LF DUO
body:
Looking for a duo preferably P1-D+
I am looking for a good ADC, because I myself was an ADC main and I don't want to be thinking that I play better than you in a role I once played.
VOIP isn't mandatory, though I would prefer it. Quiet games are boring games
If interested, add me up!

replies.body: im a really good bronze 5 adc on my smurf does that count
